{
  "stem": "18186.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 376.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I could work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they took us immediately, and they send us to this gutsverwaltung.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was a huge farm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that was in German it was gutsverwaltung.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gutsverwaltung, and-- and that was managed by German people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well he was, but he stayed there-- everyone, I think, was supposed-- was supposed to-- had to be a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I-- you know, I have the picture, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, so they took us to the gutsverwaltung.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was located between-- in a small area town, between Deutsch Krone, which was-- well let's say, and Schneidemuhl.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Schneidemuhl was the biggest city, and Deutsch Krone was a smaller town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was closer to the farm too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Deutsch Krone, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And but we stayed-- the place where we stayed was-- was-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a name that the farm, you know-- Buchenwald?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No, not Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I forgot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe it will come to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, beginning I did what all, everybody did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like the Polish people, they were also war prisoners there, Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody worked on the farm, in the field, everybody, even Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Harvesting, weeding, whatever had to be-- pick potatoes, whatever it was we had to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the-- even the Germans that were still at home, the kids, they had to work too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then-- then they took all these children, the young-- young men and women to the army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At the end of the war was this already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The end-- the end of war, we liberated '45, yeah, maybe '46, maybe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From starting from Wirke till-- from the Poland, it was probably was like four or five years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we lived together after the war a little.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we did have Christmas naturally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I celebrate their holidays.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
